sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Staf
    participant Sistem
    participant Basis Data

    Staf->>Sistem: Registrasi penghuni baru
    activate Sistem
    Sistem->>Basis Data: Cek kesediaan kamar
    activate Basis Data
    Basis Data-->>Sistem: Kamar tersedia?
    deactivate Basis Data
    
    alt Tersedia
        Sistem->>Basis Data: Simpan data tenant & leases
        activate Basis Data
        Basis Data-->>Sistem: Sukses
        deactivate Basis Data
        Sistem-->>Staf: Konfirmasi berhasil
    else Penuh
        Sistem-->>Staf: Peringatan kamar penuh
    end
    deactivate Sistem